import React from 'react'

export default function Dropdown2(props) {
  return (
    <select
      id={props.name}
      name={props.name}
      class="selectpicker"
      data-live-search="true"
    >
      <option v="january" >
        January
      </option>
      <option v="february">February</option>
      <option v="march">March</option>
      <option v="april">April</option>
      <option v="may">May</option>
      <option v="june">June</option>
      <option v="july">July</option>
      <option v="august">August</option>
      <option v="september">September</option>
      <option v="october">October</option>
      <option v="november">November</option>
      <option v="december">December</option>
    </select>
  );
}
